'''氨基甾体'''（Aminosteroid）是一类结构相似的[[甾体|甾体]]，而這些[[甾体|甾体]]的[[甾体|甾体]]核基本上都被[[胺|氨基]][[取代基|取代]]<ref name="LinSmith2016">{{Cite book|last=Ted Lin|last2=Tim Smith|last3=Colin Pinnock|title=Fundamentals of Anaesthesia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=o5y0DQAAQBAJ&pg=PA650|date=1 December 2016|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-316-66678-4|pages=650–}}</ref><ref name="LemkeWilliams2012">{{Cite book|last=Thomas L. Lemke|last2=David A. Williams|title=Foye's Principles of Medicinal Chemistry|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Sd6ot9ul-bUC&pg=PA336|date=24 January 2012|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=978-1-60913-345-0|pages=336–337|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713221044/https://books.google.com/books?id=Sd6ot9ul-bUC&pg=PA336|dead-url=no}}</ref>。氨基甾体是[[神經肌肉阻斷劑|神经肌肉阻断剂]]的成分之一，可以作为[[菸鹼型乙醯膽鹼受體|烟碱乙酰胆碱受体]]（nAChR）的[[受体拮抗剂|竞争性拮抗剂]]，阻断[[神经系统|神经系统]]中[[乙酰胆碱|乙酰胆碱]]的[[细胞信号传送|信号传导]]<ref name="Dugdale2011">{{Cite book|last=Alexandra Dugdale|title=Veterinary Anaesthesia: Principles to Practice|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0_7MRlsNbnoC&pg=PA144|date=28 November 2011|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-1-118-27933-5|pages=144–|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007211553/https://books.google.com/books?id=0_7MRlsNbnoC&pg=PA144|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WHO2013">{{Cite web |url=https://www.who.int/medicines/services/inn/StemBook_2013_Final.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2017-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809174219/http://www.who.int/medicines/services/inn/StemBook_2013_Final.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

